room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: This place was fantastic! There are a wide variety of types of puzzles to engage different brains. Darryl, our game master, was funny and engaging. They have a great system for providing as much or as little help as you need. We look forward to coming back and trying them all!

room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: This was our first time doing an escape room and we will definitely do it again! John was friendly and dressed in character for the room we did, the Cuckoo's Nest. It was fun and even though it was only 2 of us that came we still had a blast! The challenge is real!

room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: We did the Cuckoo's Nest yesterday and it was really awsome! A lot of fun!

room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: I surprised my boyfriend with tickets to the Cuckoo's Nest and we both loved it! It was our first escape room and we had a great time. I would absolutely recommend this place

room_title: Escape room "Cuckoo's Nest" by Key To Escape in Nashua
review: We went for a team event tonight with our real estate time. What a great experience. Would highly recommend and would do this again. We did the Cuckoo's Nest room. Well worth doing! Staff was extremely helpful.
